This project uses the Runescape API to pull the prices of items and
display them. It runs every day at 3pm.

Tools used:
- `Runscape API`
- `pandas` python library
- `requests` python library
- Github Actions workflow

[View the live site](https://halytus.github.io/Self-Updating-Graph/)

[View the github repo](https://github.com/Halytus/Self-Updating-Graph/tree/master)
